	   <tr><td colspan=2>OK, at 15 you get a good orc group solid group about level 17 average, maybe 16 average, (btw at that level group must be full) You hunt orcs for 8 hours and you are 18 or 19! plus these orcs drop ringmail, runes, mage and necro reasearch, bronze weapons cash ( I got 100pp plus in under 2 levels here ).&nbsp;&nbsp;AT 18 or 19 you want to get a well group in RE, this is great super fast exp, but horrible loot except for occassional large brick of hq ore (sells for about 35pp to pcs) got 2 of them in one level here) Solid group=22! At 22 get an sh group and head downstairs in RE.  Uber lewts! BA stuff sells for a lot, belt sells for up to 30pp and ba coif?  1K!!! BABS=200pp (it's 24/39!) so many great items down here, exp is 20% bonus, constant even, yellow, and red pulls, downside super dangerous! you get screwed, you have no hope!  If you have a strong group (btw 2 good tanks a cleric and an enchanter are key!) you can stay down here for hours, thriving off of the *impossible* pulls, getting levels in under 2 hours, you can stay here for a while.  At 25-28 exp starts slowing, so head to a. kunark( best exp ok loot can stay until 60) b. velious (best loot, ok exp, can stay until 60, c. warrior group in high keep ( ok loot, good exp can stay there until 35) d. mistmore (I don't know to much about mistmoore) or you could e. get a hg group in rathe mountains! (good loot, ok exp, can stay until about 35.  at about 35 you could head to sol B, guk, kith at night, named in RE, griffons, permafrost. or stay in veloius/kunark.  (BTW this is good for all race/classes<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
