	   <tr><td colspan=2>I play a 26 Wiz on saryn server, and I spent 15 thru 19th in East Karana killing gorge hounds and spiders. I also spent a little time north of there in the Gorge of King Xorrb when I got bored. Be careful in the gorge if you go there at that level though, I would suggest fighting next to the Runneye zone for a quick escape route. After you hit 19 I would head for South Karana and fight Aviaks in the Aviak town. I have been in SK for 7 fairly quick levels now, and dont plan on leaving yet, Paw is very good xps if you got a good group. Also the gnolls at the spires drop fine steel weapons (5-7pp) quite often, so the loot isnt to bad.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
