	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well, I have to say that I got major experience down doing pickclaws, but you could try to do tesch mas gnolls or aviaks in SK then move to Paw. Or you could go to mudpit in Overthere and solo, you could go Lake of Ill Omen, Stonebrunt mountains. Hell go to Lake Rathe, you will get experience in all these zones but if your looking to level to fast then you might as well give it up unless you have someone to power level. <br><br>Remember that 20th lvl is the first mini hell level you come too, you will see hell lvls from that point on. 25th is a bit slower than 20th 30th slower than 25th, 35th slower than 30th so and so on. So you may be getting good exp at 20th its just takes a bit more to fill the bubs at those levels. I just got my sk out of 40th hell few weeks ago, and my ranger is just about to level out of 45th hell. So be patient and you will see your experience fly after you get 21st.<br>&nbsp;<br>Cannis 60th Ranger<br></td></tr>
